1. *Miliona* ljudi je posetilo ovu manifestaciju. (A million people visited this event.)
2. On je zaradio *milionu* dolara. (He earned a million dollars.) 
3. Ona je provela *milion* sati učeći. (She spent a million hours learning.)
4. *Milioni* ljudi su glasali za njega. (Millions of people voted for him.)
5. *Milionima* ljudi je ovo vrlo važno. (Millions of people find this very important.)